quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Ndithudi Iye amene adalamulira Buku la Korani kuti livumbulutsidwe kwa iwe adzakubwezera kumalo komwe udzapite. Nena, “Ambuye wanga adziwa bwino iye amene amabweretsa langizo loonadi ndiponso iye amene ndi wosochera.”"
  28,86,Ndipo iwe siumayembekezera kuti Buku lolemekezeka lidzavumbulitsidwa kwa iwe koma ndi chifundo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako. Kotero usavomereze zochita za anthu omwe ali osakhulupirira
  28,87,Usalole wina aliyense kuti akubweze ku chivumbulutso cha Mulungu pamene chavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe ndipo aitane anthu kuti adze kwa Ambuye wako ndipo usakhale m’gulu la anthu amene amaphatikiza milungu ina ndi Mulungu weniweni
  28,88,Ndipo usamphatikize mulungu wina ndi Mulungu weniweni. Kulibe mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Zinthu zonse ndi zakutha kupatula Iye yekha. Chake ndi chiweruzo ndipo kwa Iye ndi kumene mudzabwerera
  29,1,Alif. Lam Mim
  29,2,"Kodi anthu amaganiza kuti adzasiyidwa okha osayesedwa chifukwa anena kuti, “Ife ndife okhulupirira?”"
  29,3,"Ndipo ndithudi Ife tidawayesa anthu amene adalipo iwo asanadze. Ndithudi Mulungu adzawazindikira iwo amene ndi olungama, ndipo ndithudi, adzawazindikira iwo amene ndi abodza"
  29,4,"Kodi kapena iwo amene amachita zoipa amaganiza kuti\tadzatithawa\tife?\tIwo\tamaweruza\tmolakwa"
  29,5,"Aliyense amene amakhulupirira kuti adzakumana ndi Mulungu nthawi imene Mulungu adakhazikitsa, ndithudi, idzabwera ndipo Iye ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa"
  29,6,"Ndipo aliyense amene adzipereka kwathunthu, akudzipereka podzithandiza iye mwini. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi woima payekha ndipo Iye safuna thandizo lochokera kwa zolengedwa zake"